Context: The George Brown College website provides a tool for users to compare up to 3 individual programs offered at the college. Users can access all programs using the Program Finder. Instructions are given on how to learn about the applications process for domestic and international students, and information about land acknowledgment is also available. Interested individuals can sign up to receive updates about application deadlines, college news, upcoming events, tours, and more. The contact details provided are a phone number (416-415-2000), a TTY number (1-877-515-5559), an email address (ask.george@georgebrown.ca), and social media hubs. The website contains information that is subject to change without notice and should not be considered as a representation, offer or warranty. Students are responsible for verifying George Brown College fee requirements.
